To the End bụ ihe nkiri America nkè afọ 2022 nkè Rachel Lears duziri

Ihe nkiri ahụ na-elekwasị anya na mgbanwe ihu igwe ma gosipụta ónyé nnọchi anya US Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez, Varshini Prakash, ónyé guzobere Sunrise Movement, Alexandra Rojas, ónyé isi nchịkwa nke Justice Democrats, na Rhiana Gunn-Wright, ónyé nduzi iwu ihu igwe màkà Roosevelt Institute
Ihe nkiri ahụ malitere na 2022 Sundance Film Festival ma gosipụta ya na Tribeca Film Festival n'ọnwa Juun n'afọ 2022.
Ọ bụ ezie na ndị nkatọ nabatara ihe nkiri ahụ nke ọma, ihe nkiri ahụ emeghị ihe a tụrụ anya ya na ụlọ ọrụ ịkụ nzọ
N'oge ngwụsị izu mbụ ya, egosiri ihe nkiri ahụ na ihuenyo otu narị na iri abụọ gafee United States, na-enweta dollar puku itoolu na narị isii na iri isii na asaa.
